<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von Wilhelms von Castell
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> wegen, als den Heinrich von
                                <expan>Kauffu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>, hauptman czu Daczaw, gefangen hat
                        etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> und danken
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> ersamkeit,
                            <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreybens</expan> und guten willens, den ir czu uns und
                                <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> habt <expan>fleissiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>;
                        und tun euch darauff czuwissen, daz der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
                        Wilhelm von Castell <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> rehter ynwonender
                                <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ist und süst
                            <expan>nymand<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>czu versprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> stet <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        uns, als wir das dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>Kauffu<ex>n</ex>g<ex>en</ex></expan> selber czu guter masz wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>zuwisse<ex>n</ex></expan> getan
                        <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir dem
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> ewr günstige <expan>furdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
                        gen dem hauptman des lantfrids Czaczer kreiszes etc. und auch
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan> von <expan>Kauffu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
                        beweisen wöllet durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz derselb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und sein <expan>pürge<ex>n</ex></expan> ledig
                        und, ob <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> icht <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> wer
                                <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>, auch wider
                            <expan>werd<ex>en</ex></expan>. Als etc. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
